<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by ShinZed:
[B]A 44 ENC would have no trouble stunning in Lguk, they have all the spells if their research is up to snuff. Nothing in Lguk is all that resistant.

For the low level AoE group, you don't need stuns as much as a higher level group, given that your casters can actually withstand a good few rounds of combat if they are decently equipped. Of course, snagging a 20+ enchanter (has 2 stuns) would be a huge boon.  :)[/B][/QUOTE]

